Sentencas: State-of-the-art nickel-based SOFC anode-supported cells are highly sensitive to reoxidation of the metal phase at the temperature of utilization.
Titulo: Redox stable Ni-YSZ anode support in solid oxide fuel cell stack configuration

Sentencas: This work presents results on redox stable nickel-YSZ (yttria-stabilized zirconia) anode-supported cells, for both smaller and larger scale cells.
Titulo: Redox stable Ni-YSZ anode support in solid oxide fuel cell stack configuration

Sentencas: A 55 cm(2) cell was mounted in a SOFC stack repeat element and tested over 40 full redox cycles.
Titulo: Redox stable Ni-YSZ anode support in solid oxide fuel cell stack configuration

Sentencas: Performances and electrochemical impedance results of the repeat element are compared to the smaller sized cells of similar anode support structure.
Titulo: Redox stable Ni-YSZ anode support in solid oxide fuel cell stack configuration
